388", "name": "cloud", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_normal.png?m=1678761388", "title": "云计算", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/cloud", "topics": 5475, "footer": "", "header": "关于云计算技术和平台的综合讨论区。", "title_alternative": "Cloud Computing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_mini.png?m=1678761388", "stars": 3228, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 104, "parent_node_name": "webmaster"}, "member": {"id": 605098, "username": "okkkk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/okkkk", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bb69/09d6/605098_mini.png?m=1747656641", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bb69/09d6/605098_normal.png?m=1747656641", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bb69/09d6/605098_large.png?m=1747656641", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bb69/09d6/605098_xlarge.png?m=1747656641", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bb69/09d6/605098_xlarge.png?m=1747656641", "created": 1670377533, "last_modified": 1747656641}, "last_reply_by": "Light3", "last_touched": 1747488164, "title": "吐槽阿里云，把我用了十年的网站备案吊销了。。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1136138", "created": 1748952747, "deleted": 0, "content": "我把网站迁到腾讯云上面（都一两年了）\r\n\r\n最近有一天给我打电话\r\n\r\n说让我把服务迁回阿里云，因为备案的时候用的是阿里云服务。\r\n\r\n我也没在意，因为十年间也用过别人的云服务业没啥问题。\r\n\r\n结果。。。\r\n\r\n真给我备案直接注销了\r\n\r\n导致我迁域名回国内服务商+重新备案。\r\n\r\n至少两周多服务没办法使用。\r\n\r\n真是恶心到我了。。。。", "content_rendered": "<p>我把网站迁到腾讯云上面（都一两年了）</p>\n<p>最近有一天给我打电话</p>\n<p>说让我把服务迁回阿里云，因为备案的时候用的是阿里云服务。</p>\n<p>我也没在意，因为十年间也用过别人的云服务业没啥问题。</p>\n<p>结果。。。</p>\n<p>真给我备案直接注销了</p>\n<p>导致我迁域名回国内服务商+重新备案。</p>\n<p>至少两周多服务没办法使用。</p>\n<p>真是恶心到我了。。。。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1748953088, "replies": 49, "id": 1136138}]